[Student "S"]
{NORTH has 15 points, a singleton in the opponent's suit and 4-card support for any suit 
partner might name. In other words, a perfect Takeout Double.

SOUTH needs to make a medium-strong bid to apprise NORTH of her 10 points. She jumps to 2\S.

NORTH's hand is now worth 17 points because of the singleton. Since he is quite happy with 
\Ss he bids 4\S.}

